column4: Instructions

Hello! This spreadsheet will show current information and historical data for a specifed stock and the Dow Jones, NASDAQ, and S&P 500 Indexes. To use this spreadsheet, simply edit the YELLOW cells and the rest of the sheet will update automatically.Start and End Dates correspond to the scope of Historical Data at the bottom of the sheet.NOTE - For Stock Symbol, Enter a company's Stock Symbol (Ex. AAPL) and for Start and End Date use YYYY-MM-DD (Ex. 2019-01-07).
